歲及18歲</span>，警方早前接獲報案，指他們於上周日及上周二遭一名南亞漢非禮，案發於東堤灣畔的行人隧道及東涌新發展碼頭，<span style=\"color: red;\">當時南亞漢走近身旁搭訕，期間借故吻面，同時伸手觸下體，南亞漢亦伺機露出下體，逼令事主為其口交，於得嚐獸慾後逃去。</span><br />\n<br />\n案件交由大嶼山警區刑事部接手調查，警方翻查附近的閉路電視錄影展開追查，掌握涉案南亞色魔容貌，經深入調查後，上周五晚上8時，在大嶼北將涉嫌非禮的巴基斯坦籍男子(34歲)拘捕，他持有香港身份證，報稱任職地盤工人。警方相信可能有更多區內少年受害，呼籲任何目擊案件人士或受害人，請即與警方聯絡。"},{"pid":"06966df360a3831a9cc669b8d2245dff486d1544","tid":450270,"uid":78392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T13:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港女仲要係全亞洲最差"},{"pid":"4d39ef13fb21b8b5e5321fb977881edc5b3f7fd9","tid":450270,"uid":100150,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T15:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港女仲要係全亞洲最差</blockquote><br />\n港女有能力同優秀白人結合生優良嘅下一代<br />\n黃種男性做唔到"},{"pid":"59162a1e5b6abfc7b017a04737e0893ccdb4aadd","tid":450270,"uid":78392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:40:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港女仲要係全亞洲最差</blockquote><br />\n港女有能力同優秀白人結合生優良嘅下一代<br />\n黃種男性做唔到</blockquote><br />\n肯食劣質港女既白人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔方優秀得去邊"},{"pid":"dd1489503d8776641e6bf823120e2ec29b4aadf0","tid":450270,"uid":54733,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy